<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- (tkẖṭyṭk rạỷʿ lḥyạtnạ .. wlạ ymkn ạ̉bdaⁿạ tgẖlṭ
 mn kl klạmk ạlṣạlḥ .. msẖ mmkn klmẗ htsqṭ)2
 (ʿạrf ạ̹yh ạlạ̉fḍl lynạ .. kl ḥyạtnạ mʿạk fy ạ̉mạn
 ḥạsẖạ fy ywm ạ̹nk tw̉dẖynạ .. klh lkẖyrnạ mhmạ ạ̹n kạn)2
 klh lkẖyrnạ mhmạ ạ̹n kạn
 2- (ṣạlḥ dạymaⁿạ mhmạ byḥṣl .. ʿạrf ạ̹nt btʿml ạ̹yh
 qṣdk dạymaⁿạ hw ạlạ̉fḍl .. lyk ạlḥkmẗ fy ạ̹mty̱ wlyh)2
 (lyk fy ạlmwt ạ̉ktr mn mkẖrj .. wbtgẖyr ạ̉wqạt wạ̉zmạn
 wmn ạljạfy ḥlạwẗ btkẖrj .. wḥdk lyk kl ạlslṭạn)2
 wḥdk lyk kl ạlslṭạn
 3- (ʿynk dạymaⁿạ ʿ ạlly ykẖạfk .. wạlly bytrjy̱ mrạḥmk
 ʿndk rḥmẗ wkẖyr lwlạdk .. ṣạlḥ wktyrẗ ạ̉mạntk)2
 (fkrk dạymaⁿạ mn nạḥytnạ .. kẖyr wslạm wạlậkẖrẗ rjạʾ
 wbtḥmlnạ fy ṭwl sktnạ .. wʿndk lynạ yạ rb sẖfạʾ)2
 ʿndk lynạ yạ rb sẖfạʾ
 4- (ạ̹nt ạ̹lh ạlqdrẗ wmljạ̉ .. fy rʿạytk tḥml wtṣwn
 wbydk trsm ạ̉yạmnạ .. mstqblnạ mʿạk mḍmwn)2
 (rạsm kl ạlʿmr wʿạrf .. kl ạlkẖyr lḥyạtnạ mnyn
 lmạ bntʿb wḥdk sẖạyf .. tqdr tsnd mạ ạ̹nt mʿyn)2
 tqdr tsnd mạ ạ̹nt mʿyn</lyrics>
<title>tkẖṭyṭk rạỷʿ lḥyạtnạ</title>
<author>bạsm rsẖdy̱, bhjt ʿdly</author>
